# 🧠 Memory Card Game

A simple Memory Card Game built with **HTML, CSS and JavaScript**.

## 🎮 Features

- Flip cards
- Match two identical cards
- Move counter
- Timer
- Restart game
- Win notification
- Responsive design

## 🛠 Technologies

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (Vanilla)

